      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 17:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>NFL 的“比尔黑手党”利用市政债券为新体育场提供融资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/nfl-s-bills-mafia-tapped-to-finance-new-stadium-with-muni-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布法罗比尔队最忠实的球迷被称为“比尔帮”，他们以向球队伸出援手而闻名，今年早些时候他们清理了 NFL 球队主场的积雪，为季后赛做准备。现在，这些狂热粉丝有机会为球队耗资 17 亿美元的新主场提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/nfl-s-bills-mafia-tapped-to-finance-new-stadium-with-muni-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 16:20:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉美货币领跌新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/emerging-stocks-extend-drop-as-nvidia-dampens-ai-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，拉丁美洲货币下跌，因为新数据显示美国经济走强，推高了美国国债收益率。墨西哥和巴西的政治担忧加剧了这一走势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/emerging-stocks-extend-drop-as-nvidia-dampens-ai-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 11:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
